==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stormglass
<hw>Storm"glass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A glass vessel,
usually cylindrical, filled with a solution which is sensitive to
atmospheric changes, indicating by a clouded appearance, rain, snow,
etc., and by clearness, fair weather.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stormily</ent>⟦br⟧
